snippet.title: Cubes and more cubes - trailer
snippet.description:
An interesting game with many levels and interesting gameplay. Frequent updates and themed updates such as "winter", "halloween", "new year", etc. will not make you bored. 
With each update, many interesting levels are added to the game.
Convenient interface, even a small child can figure it out.
And that is not all! Take your friends and go faster levels!

- download game -  https://dankoff.itch.io/cubes-and-more-cubes
